reviewText: Taroko is probably the sound the rooster makes. Hawaii has a Kaloko dam on Kauai Island and a Kaloko national park on the big island of Hawaii. Truuk Island or Chuuk is probably the same name spelled differently.
SEEMS LIKE A MATURE EDITING - exposure ok but  scenes repeat  storey simplistic.
i have been there many times. The DVDgives a proper impression but is too short
